Simple shopping cart implementation with test pay2go



Steps

1. Adding gems
gem 'devise'
gem 'annotate'
gem 'carrierwave'
gem 'mini_magick'
gem 'bootstrap-sass'


2.Generate Category name
3.Generate Product name price category:referces
4.Change root route
5.Run db seed
6.change category_id to category options in product form
7.Generate asset with image:string and belongs to product
8.Create image carrierwave    Follow: https://code.tutsplus.com/tutorials/rails-image-upload-using-carrierwave-in-a-rails-app--cms-25183
9.Give up Try add image column to product (改天再試Assets)
10.Create Cart model and controller
11.Create CartItem model with cart_id and product_id
